larrikinism
Homonym Number:
Word Class:noun
Sense Number:
Definition:rowdy, objectionable public behaviour; also humorously applied to children's or adolescents' behaviour.
Origin:[none]
Register:
Register 2:
Domain:[none]
Region:[none]
